      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>A bill to amend title 40, United States Code, to provide the Marshal of the Supreme Court of the United States and Supreme Court Police with the authority to protect the Chief Justice of the United States, any Associate Justice of the Supreme Court, and other individuals in any location, and for other purposes.</title>
        <billTextVersionName>Introduced in Senate</billTextVersionName>
